com.facebook.buck.skylark.parser

Class IncludesData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.skylark.parser.IncludesData

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value="org.immutables.processor.ProxyProcessor")
 @Immutable
 @CheckReturnValue
public final class IncludesData
extends Object
    Captures information related to all included extensions used in order to load the main build spec. The main purpose of extra information is to properly capture all dependent information to obtain the loaded files without full execution of the build spec.
